          <div class="card-body events">
            <h5 class="card-title events text-center">Funeral Services</h5>
            <p class="card-text text-left">
            THE TRANSFORMATION OF LIFE WITH A CARING PASTOR<br>
            <br>
            Don’t desert the one who is dying, advises Pastor Tony Freitas of A & Z God's Ministry for All People. The person who is dying usually knows that he or she is dying, and the secret for us is not to be afraid of that or to run away from it. Ask them what they’re thinking about, what they may need. Often, our emotions mirror those of the person with whom we are talking. In those moments, one wounded heart reaches out to another, and they connect. That can be a beautiful experience, Just holding hands and praying.<br>
            </p>
