          <div class="card-body events">
            <h5 class="card-title events text-center">Indoor and Outdoor Weddings</h5>
            <p class="card-text text-left">
            Do you want an Indoor or Outdoor Wedding?<br>
            <br>
            When a bride and groom begin to plan their wedding they should think about all of the wedding options. A wedding style is something that every wedding has. No, it is not “stylish”- it is a style. Do you envision your wedding being outdoors or indoors? Along those same lines, what kind of venue do you envision your wedding taking place at?<br>
            <br>
            Married on the beach, in the park, on the mountains, or in your backyard, ring exchange or ring ceremony, indoor or outdoor. English or Portuguese it is your choice.<br>
            <br>
            MORNING WEDDING, EARLY AFTERNOON WEDDING, LATER EVENING WEDDING<br>
            <br>
            Having Pastor Tony Freitas officiate your wedding is to have a CHRISTIAN WEDDING CEREMONY or just a simple wedding. Your marriage must stand by the strength of your love and the power of faith in each other and in God. We can do indoor or outdoor. It is all about the two of you.<br>
            <br>
            Whichever option you choose though, your wedding day will be amazing!
